The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS are conducting several roadblocks across Cape Town. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS discovered a stash of contraband cigarettes in Cape Town. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS conduct several roadblocks in the Western Cape. Three people have been arrested here for violating the regulations InTembisa. A man in the Western Cape has been detained after Cape Town Metro Police found a stash of cigarettes. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS are conducting several roadblocks across Cape Town. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS discovered a stash of contraband cigarettes in Cape Town. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS conduct several roadblocks in the Western Cape. Three people have been arrested here for violating the regulations InTembisa. A man in the Western Cape has been detained after Cape Town Metro Police found a stash of cigarettes. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS are conducting several roadblocks across Cape Town. The Cape Town Metro Police, together with the SANDF and SAPS discovered a stash of contraband cigarettes in Cape Town.